*.zip

# Android native project: the SOURCE is tracked (versionCode/versionName, the
# manifest, app icons and splash art) because `cap sync` never regenerates it -
# a fresh clone running `cap add android` would get a default project and lose
# all of it. Only build output, machine-local paths and signing secrets are out.
